  "title": "Warehouse Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>· Updating of stock to server/computer</p><p>· Perform accurate monthly stock check, organize all items</p><p>· Prepare, arrange and distribute products according to pack list.</p><p>· Sorts and places products on racks, shelves, or in bins</p><p>· Receive and verify accuracy of incoming shipments, proper filing</p><p>· Pick and pack high-value products</p><p>· Maintain daily timelines to ensure all tasks are accomplished on time.</p><p>· Other Ad-hoc duties as assigned<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>· <strong>Experience:</strong> 1–2 years of experience in storekeeping, logistics, or warehouse operations preferred.</p><p>· <strong>Skills:</strong></p><p>a. Basic computer literacy (Microsoft Excel, inventory systems).</p><p>b. Ability to operate warehouse equipment (forklift etc.).</p><p>c. Strong attention to detail and accuracy in record-keeping.</p><p>· <strong>Physical Requirements:</strong> Able to lift or move moderately heavy items when necessary.</p><p>· <strong>Added advantage</strong>: Possess Class 3 Driver's License</p>",
